txt.en: Talk to Klúso near Stazg Vozag

'There are several sentries on the roads around here, coming and going from the out-camp. Removing them will hinder any schemes the hobgoblins might think up, and also lower the chance that one of them might stumble upon our own camp.\n\n'You know what to do, [placeholder].'
Hobgoblin sentries patrol the roads near Stazg Vozag.
'You cleared the roads? Good work. At the very least it will be easier to sneak out of here when we're done.\n\n'Oh yes, my friend. We are just getting started!'
Klúso is scouting near Stazg Vozag.
Hobgoblin sentries patrol the road near the out-camp of Stazg Vozag.
